reviewText: My daughter is 2 1/2 and the first day we had this video she watched it like 3 times!  It's very cute and funny, very informative, easy to listen to and easy to watch.  I'm planning on getting some of the other Henry the Lizard videos too.  Henry is an animated lizard, but the animals are real.  There are some parts that are cartoon-ish.  I highly recommend this video when you want to watch something is that soothing.  And there are NO COMMERCIALS!!!  Yeah!
